members.name: keyword
members.doc: `Required`, Suggested keyword

members.name: volume
members.doc: `Required`, The average number of times users have searched for a given keyword, for given month

members.name: difficulty
members.doc: `Required`, An estimate of how difficult it would be to rank well in organic search results for a particular keyword. The higher the percentage, the harder it is to achieve high rankings for the given keyword

members.name: latestTrends
members.doc: `Required`, The interest of searchers in a particular keyword during the last 12 months, while first value is 12 month ago, and last is 1 month ago

members.name: searcherIntent
members.doc: Keyword intent (optional)

members.name: quota
members.doc: User quota information

members.name: remaining
members.doc: Amount of quota left until renew date

members.name: limit
members.doc: Total amount of quota user has

members.name: startDate
members.doc: Start time for current quota

members.name: endDate
members.doc: End time for current quota, once pass quota will be reset

members.name: paidPlan
members.doc: In case false, user will be shown an option to upgrade using the upgrade_url

docs.summary:
Possible values are:
  • UNKNOWN
  • COMMERCIAL - users want to hybrid of informational and transactional, like research before making a purchase decision
  • INFORMATIONAL - user wants to learn something
  • NAVIGATIONAL - User wants to find a specific page, domain, or physical address
  • TRANSACTIONAL - users want to do something specific, either in person or using their device

Possible values are:
  • UNKNOWN
  • NOT_INSTALLED - App is not installed on site
  • PENDING_CONFIGURATIONS - user need to finish configurations
  • INSTALLED - App is installed and configured
